    }}>{`Concept`}</h2>
    <p>{`Data & Statistics are an essencial part of Mathium. Mathium allows you to find the mean, median, mode, rande, and standard deviation in one line of code. This function uses `}<strong parentName="p">{`these formulas to work:`}</strong></p>
