    <p>{`Suppose we have an array of `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`[1, 2.25, 3.5, 4.75, 6, 7.25, 8.5]`}</inlineCode>{` and we want to find the median of the data.
When applying the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`dataStatCall`}</inlineCode>{`, the result would be the following:`}</p>
